The paper deals with a wiretap channel, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT) and cryptography (cs.CR). The use of multiple antennas by the sender, receiver, and eavesdropper falls under the category of multiple-input multiple-output (MIMO) systems, which is a topic in multimedia (cs.MM) and networking (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the conditions for secure communication, which is a topic in security and privacy (cs.SI).
